doc.after: The country is mostly savannah although the moist and mountainous east supports tropical evergreen and hardwood forests Trees include teak and mahogany knobthorn msasa and baobab Among the numerous flowers and shrubs are hibiscus spider lily leonotus cassia tree wisteria and dombeya
